    <string name="notes_code_99_title">Version 2.5.0: Tor changes</string>
    <string name="notes_code_99_body">Enabling Tor now requires installing a third-party Tor Proxy VPN app such as Orbot.\n\nThis makes background payments much more reliable with Tor.\n\nAlso Phoenix now always uses onion addresses for Lightning and Electrum connections when Tor is enabled..</string>
